flowchart TD
    A[Start Scan] --> B{QR Data Valid?}
    B -- No --> C[Return Invalid Result]
    B -- Yes --> D{Cooldown Active?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Return Blocked Result]
    D -- No --> F[Resolve Student Profile]
    F --> G{Scan Mode}
    G -->|Entry Only| H[Set Action Entry]
    G -->|Exit Only| I[Set Action Exit]
    G -->|Both| J[Prompt Action Entry or Exit]
    H --> K[Record Attendance]
    I --> K
    J --> K
    K --> L{Record Success?}
    L -- No --> M[Return Blocked/Invalid Message]
    L -- Yes --> N[Update Analytics]
    N --> O[Return Success Result]
